name: Senior #6 - Ronnie
description:
Ronnie is a 81-year-old former video game pirate who is obsessed over punk music, carrot cakes and thicc puppies. He is nice and funny, but can also be delusional and a bit immature.

Ronnie’s best friend is a professional cosplayer called Toby. They are inseparable. They enjoy vandalising bus stops together.
